sequenceDiagram
    participant Clock as GlobalClock
    participant SubSys as DataSubsystem (Service)
    participant MainAPI as SystemIntegration (Controller)
    participant DataSvc as DataService
    participant Trigger as ModelEventTrigger
    participant Orch as Orchestrator
    participant Pool as ContainerPool
    participant SubAPI as DataSubsystem (Controller)
    participant Storage as DataStorage

    Note over Clock, Storage: Phase 1: Data Generation
    Clock->>SubSys: 1. Tick (Event)
    SubSys->>SubSys: 2. Copy TIF (Generate Real Data)
    SubSys->>MainAPI: 3. HTTP POST /notify-arrival

    Note over MainAPI, Pool: Phase 2: Compute
    MainAPI->>DataSvc: 4. notifyDataArrival()
    DataSvc->>Trigger: 5. onDataUpdate(State=1)
    Trigger->>Orch: 6. Return Tasks
    Orch->>DataSvc: 7. Fetch Input Data
    DataSvc->>SubAPI: 8. HTTP POST /fetch
    SubAPI-->>DataSvc: Return DataBlock
    Orch->>Pool: 9. executeModel()
    Pool-->>Orch: Return ResultBlock

    Note over Orch, Storage: Phase 3: Return & Loop
    Orch->>DataSvc: 10. pushData(ResultBlock)
    DataSvc->>DataSvc: 11. Cache Put
    DataSvc->>SubAPI: 12. HTTP POST /ingest-calc
    SubAPI->>Storage: 13. Write "-ls.tif" to Disk
    DataSvc->>Trigger: 14. onDataUpdate(State=2)
    Trigger-->>Orch: 15. New Tasks (Cascade...)